        <abstract>
            <p>Is writing his paper on orchids.</p> 
<p>Is surprised that AG gets little or no response with <hi rend="italic">Drosera</hi>.</p>  
<p>Describes the two forms of <hi rend="italic">Primula</hi> and asks whether AG knows any analogous cases of dimorphism.</p> 
            <p>Reports that John Stuart Mill approves of CD’s scientific method.</p>
            <p>Discusses American politics.</p>
        </abstract>
